sndlib.core.model
Enum ModelProperty

java.lang.Object
  java.lang.Enum<ModelProperty>
      sndlib.core.model.ModelProperty
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<ModelProperty>
public enum ModelProperty
extends java.lang.Enum<ModelProperty>

This enum is used to identify the submodels constituting a network Model.

Each of the submodel identifiers corresponds to a enumeration class declaring the submodel values.

Author:
Roman Klaehne
